WEBVTT

1
01:08:21.380 --> 01:08:24.570 
依着山  包藏着黑暗
stands against its hills holding darkness within.

2
01:08:26.460 --> 01:08:28.470 
它会在此伫立一百年
It has stood so for a hundred years

3
01:08:28.470 --> 01:08:30.450 
可能两百年
and might stand a hundred more.

4
01:08:36.390 --> 01:08:37.210 
房子里
Within...

5
01:08:38.020 --> 01:08:42.590 
墙壁依旧直立  砖头严丝合缝
walls continue upright... bricks meet neatly...

6
01:08:43.190 --> 01:08:44.720 
地板牢固
floors are firm...

7
01:08:46.480 --> 01:08:48.590 
门紧闭着
and doors are sensibly shut.

8
01:08:51.950 --> 01:08:56.730 
希尔大宅的石木间寂静无声
Silence lay steadily against the wood and stone of Hill House.

